_sText:
This is my very first map, it currently has 16 spawn points (8 for each team), the bomb is planted in a van in the middle of the map (see screenshot), both teams have a buyzone, there are also some destructible physics items.

if there is anything you would like me to change, feel free to post it here. Please provide me with constructive criticism though.

Do not modify or redistribute this map without asking for my permission fist (PM me)
